snippet.title: Umineko no Naku Koro ni Saku PS4/Switch OP - Kasaneawase no Nekobako
snippet.description:
Opening movie of Umineko no Naku Koro ni Saku ~Nekobako to Musou no Koukyoukyoku~ (PS4/Switch). Song title: "Kasaneawase no Nekobako" (重ね合わせの猫箱)

Game website: http://entergram.co.jp/umineko/
Release date: January 28th, 2021 (Japan)
